.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, chaman, ritmeester, montecristo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the montecristo-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the montecristo-smoker is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the blend-smoker##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Cigar   | ritmeester  | montecristo      | blend        | chaman     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
City: london, edinburgh, colone, hamburg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person traveling to colone is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| City   | london   | hamburg   | colone | edinburgh |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

