.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, eggplant, carrot, kale
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
4. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Food           | kale | eggplant | raspberry   | carrot |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

