.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, cola, tea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, superhero
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the tram is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
4. the person drinking cola is the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the person watching family movies is the person driving the tram##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage      | cola      | almond-milk | 7up     | tea    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family      | mystery | satire |
| Transport           | roller   | tram  | ship     | snowmobile |

