The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, surfing, swimming, water-polo
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, car, snowmobile
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
2. the person who's sport is baseball is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
5. the person watching family movies is between the person driving the bike and the person who's sport is swimming##2
6. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre    | thriller    | family     | documentary    | martial-arts        |
| Sport       | swimming   | baseball | surfing | water-polo |
| Transport   | snowmobile | car      | bike    | airplane   |

