.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, satire, sports, zombie
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, indie, jazz
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, coral, lavender, ivory
1. the person who likes ivory is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes pink is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person watching adventure movies is the person who likes pink##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
7. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | satire | adventure | sports   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | jazz   | indie     | blues    |
| Color   | coral  | lavender | pink  | ivory |

